        <title>how to batch remove the Chinese in the document</title>
        <link>https://www.stepbystep.cf/en/archives/remove-chinese-character/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 22 Mar 2022 17:20:12 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.stepbystep.cf/en/archives/remove-chinese-character/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://img.gejiba.com/images/24573291207ff1f08c2a9a343cfe7925.webp" alt="Featured image of post how to batch remove the Chinese in the document" /&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;open the document to be processed with word&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ctrl+A select all documents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ctrl+H open the replace window
! &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://img.gejiba.com/images/4d9859f12162c00796d4c436ff3a802d.webp&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Snipaste_20220322_172443.png&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click More in the bottom left corner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure &amp;ldquo;Use wildcards&amp;rdquo; is checked&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code&gt;[! ^1-^127]&lt;/code&gt; (English state input)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leave the Replace box blank&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &amp;ldquo;Replace all&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
